	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Aug 22nd 9:53 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[1.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Dere 2 problemz with dis. One fear and darkness take a lot of mana. At least from Trollz(me) and Ogrez. Cauze us not have much intelligence. My first success with fear kitin waz at lvl 26. Second problem iz dat fear wearz off fast. I usually have to cast 4-5 fears and about 2 darknesses before mob dies(At lvl 26 I waz outta manna before mob waz dead). Yet I have to agree dat fear kiting enablez uz to kill very strong mobz dat we can't kill by simply meleeing dem. Like cyclopses, HG's and SG's.<br><br>Kagek Dahungry<br>Lvl 35 Troll SK.<br>T'Vyl Honor Guard<br>Lanys T'Vyl server.<br><br>PS: I don't get much interrupts on fear at my level.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
